---
title: Chicken & Eat Smart® Sweet Kale Salad with Garlic Bread
description: How does spiced and seared chicken, tender greens, tangy-sweet dressing, and homemade garlic bread sound? Now, what if we told you that could all be on your table in just 15 minutes—no prepping or chopping required? For this satisfying and flavorful dinner, we season the chicken cutlets with a smoky cinnamon paprika spice blend, then sear until browned, thinly slice, and serve over the greens for savory contrast to the dressing. The garlic bread on the side couldn’t be simpler to make, and adds a buttery richness to the dish that just can’t be beat.
